-- üèÉ ‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏ß (‡∏°‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠/PC ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ)
local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local player = Players.LocalPlayer
local PlayerGui = player:WaitForChild("PlayerGui")

-- GUI ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å
local ScreenGui = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
ScreenGui.Name = "SpeedMenu"
ScreenGui.ResetOnSpawn = false
ScreenGui.Parent = PlayerGui

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π (‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏°‡∏∏‡∏°‡∏Ç‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏ö‡∏ô)
local OpenButton = Instance.new("TextButton")
OpenButton.Name = "OpenButton"
OpenButton.Size = UDim2.new(0, 100, 0, 40)
OpenButton.Position = UDim2.new(1, -110, 0, 10)
OpenButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 0, 0)
OpenButton.Text = "‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π"
OpenButton.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
OpenButton.TextScaled = true
OpenButton.Parent = ScreenGui

-- ‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
local MenuFrame = Instance.new("Frame")
MenuFrame.Name = "MenuFrame"
MenuFrame.Size = UDim2.new(0, 250, 0, 170)
MenuFrame.Position = UDim2.new(0.5, -125, 0.5, -85)
MenuFrame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 0, 0)
MenuFrame.Visible = false
MenuFrame.Parent = ScreenGui
MenuFrame.BorderSizePixel = 2
MenuFrame.Active = true
MenuFrame.Draggable = true

-- ‡∏´‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠
local Title = Instance.new("TextLabel")
Title.Parent = MenuFrame
Title.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 40)
Title.Text = "‚ö° ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÑ‡∏ß ‚ö°"
Title.BackgroundTransparency = 1
Title.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
Title.TextScaled = true

-- ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏ß
local SpeedBox = Instance.new("TextBox")
SpeedBox.Parent = MenuFrame
SpeedBox.Size = UDim2.new(0.8, 0, 0, 40)
SpeedBox.Position = UDim2.new(0.1, 0, 0.45, -20)
SpeedBox.PlaceholderText = "‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏ß (‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô 50, 100)"
SpeedBox.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 150, 150)
SpeedBox.TextColor3 = Color3.new(0, 0, 0)
SpeedBox.TextScaled = true

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏¢‡∏∑‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏ô
local ConfirmButton = Instance.new("TextButton")
ConfirmButton.Parent = MenuFrame
ConfirmButton.Size = UDim2.new(0.4, 0, 0, 40)
ConfirmButton.Position = UDim2.new(0.3, 0, 0.7, 0)
ConfirmButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 255, 0)
ConfirmButton.Text = "‡∏¢‡∏∑‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏ô"
ConfirmButton.TextColor3 = Color3.new(0, 0, 0)
ConfirmButton.TextScaled = true

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
local CloseButton = Instance.new("TextButton")
CloseButton.Parent = MenuFrame
CloseButton.Size = UDim2.new(0.3, 0, 0, 30)
CloseButton.Position = UDim2.new(0.65, 0, 0, 10)
CloseButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(200, 0, 0)
CloseButton.Text = "‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î"
CloseButton.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
CloseButton.TextScaled = true

-- ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡πÅ‡∏õ‡∏£
local menuOpen = false
local defaultSpeed = 16

-- ‡∏Å‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î/‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
OpenButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	menuOpen = not menuOpen
	MenuFrame.Visible = menuOpen
end)

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏° "‡∏¢‡∏∑‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏ô" ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏ß
ConfirmButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	local speedValue = tonumber(SpeedBox.Text)
	local char = player.Character or player.CharacterAdded:Wait()
	local humanoid = char:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid")
	if humanoid then
		if speedValue and speedValue > 0 then
			humanoid.WalkSpeed = speedValue
			ConfirmButton.Text = "‚úÖ ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô " .. speedValue
			task.wait(1)
			ConfirmButton.Text = "‡∏¢‡∏∑‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏ô"
		else
			ConfirmButton.Text = "‚ö†Ô∏è ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏Ç!"
			task.wait(1.2)
			ConfirmButton.Text = "‡∏¢‡∏∑‡∏ô‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏ô"
		end
	end
end)

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
CloseButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	menuOpen = false
	MenuFrame.Visible = false
end)
